{"tid":2249473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港大學生會《格物》展覽　展示反送中物品","createTime":"2020-10-19T11:01:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T16:49:32.000Z","uid":41705,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"150e21ef5434891f0bf11131c3844c9dff9c5a69","tid":2249473,"uid":41705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:01:44.000Z","msg":"【港大學生會《格物》展覽 展示反送中物品】<br />\n<br />\n港大學生會與團體「物敍」舉辦了名為《格物》的展覽，由今日起至 10 月 31 日，於香港大學學生會大樓展出一系列與香港反送中運動有關的藏品。現場可見，展出的物品包括是在警察制服上的非官方繡章，印有抗爭口號的「黃店」收據等。<br />\n<br />\n展覽簡介稱，部分展品是在遊行集會現場收集的，其餘的是由他人捐贈，「儘管這些物件的種類紛繁，它們能回應共同的目的 &mdash; 成為連接過去與現在的窗口，述說香港人故事的同時，為香港人發聲」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/122119172_3569322239820037_1562312984269256987_o.png?_nc_cat=105&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=VLIzNNoaHVMAX9U70lD&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=f45b86f0c3baa49ad47e8c70bd817901&amp;oe=5FB1A4C5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F122119172_3569322239820037_1562312984269256987_o.png%3F_nc_cat%3D105%26_nc_sid%3D730e14%26_nc_ohc%3DVLIzNNoaHVMAX9U70lD%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3Df45b86f0c3baa49ad47e8c70bd817901%26oe%3D5FB1A4C5&h=326184ed&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/122052417_3569322153153379_5427011651074162280_o.png?_nc_cat=105&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=7Vqx7SWRblwAX98h9Tv&amp;tn=mQiqTG7HEyohgP-e&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=8b38221955dce5eb1e67e8717d735b55&amp;oe=5FB44603\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F122052417_3569322153153379_5427011651074162280_o.png%3F_nc_cat%3D105%26_nc_sid%3D730e14%26_nc_ohc%3D7Vqx7SWRblwAX98h9Tv%26tn%3DmQiqTG7HEyohgP-e%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3D8b38221955dce5eb1e67e8717d735b55%26oe%3D5FB44603&h=571d5ca1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/121834664_3569322399820021_7082514495192